    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi, you'll need to set the root level of your hierarchical attribute in [`attributesToHighlight`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/api-parameters/attributesToHighlight/?client=javascript) in order to retrieve highlights for sub levels, for example:\r\n\r\n```jsx\r\n<InstantSearch>\r\n  <Configure attributesToHighlight={['metadata']} /> {/* This can also be done in the Dashboard */}\r\n  <Hits hitComponent={HitComponent} />\r\n</InstantSearch>\r\n\r\n// ...\r\n\r\nfunction HitComponent({ hit }) {\r\n  return <div>\r\n    <Highlight attribute=\"metadata.publisher\" hit={hit} />\r\n  </div>;\r\n}\r\n```",
